videos.description: The Bearcats get off to a hot start against Houston thanks to Jeremiah Davenport's pair of 3-pointers.

videos.headline: Jeremiah Davenport hits back-to-back 3s for Cincinnati

videos.description: Houston's Jamal Shead shows off his handles with a sweet behind-the-back pass to J'Wan Roberts for the lay-in.

videos.description: Houston's Kyler Edwards cuts into Cincinnati's lead with a pretty move under the basket.
